{"ID":270286, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"286\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs285.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs287.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 286<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">THE PROPHET ON THE SECOND COMING OF CHRIST<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Remarks at the Conference of the Church<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The question has been asked, can a person not belonging to the Church bring a member before\n  the high council for trial?<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> I answer, No. If I had not actually got into this work and been called of\n  God,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> I would back out. But I cannot back out:<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> I have no doubt of the truth.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> Were I going to\n  prophesy, I would say the end [of the world] would not come in 1844, 5, or 6, or in forty years.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span>\n  There are those of the rising generation<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> who shall not taste death till Christ comes.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I was once praying earnestly upon this subject, and a voice said unto me, &ldquo;My son, if thou livest\n  until thou art eighty-five years of age, thou shalt see the face of the Son of Man.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> I was left to draw\n  my own conclusions concerning this; and I took the liberty to conclude that if I did live to that time,\n  He would make His appearance. But I do not say whether He will make His appearance or I shall\n  go where He is. I prophesy in the name of the Lord God,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> and let it be written&mdash;the Son of Man will\n  not come in the clouds of heaven<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> till I am eighty-five years old.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> Then read the 14th chapter of\n  Revelation, 6th and 7th verses&mdash;&ldquo;And I saw another angel fly in the midst of heaven, having the\n  everlasting gospel to preach unto them that dwell on the earth, and to every nation, and kindred, and\n  tongue, and people, saying with a loud voice, Fear God and give glory to Him, for the hour of His\n  judgment is come.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> And Hosea, 6th chapter, After two days,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> etc.,&mdash;2,520 years; which brings it\n  to 1890. The coming of the Son of Man<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> never will be&mdash;never can be till the judgments spoken of\n  for this hour are poured out:<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> which judgments are commenced. Paul says, &ldquo;Ye are the children of\n  the light, and not of the darkness, that that day should overtake you as a thief in the night.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> It is not\n  the design of the Almighty to come upon the earth and crush it and grind it to powder,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> but he will\n  reveal it to His servants the prophets.<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Judah must return,<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> Jerusalem must be rebuilt,<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> and the temple,<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> and water come out from\n  under the temple,<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> and the waters of the Dead Sea be healed.<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> It will take some time to rebuild the\n  walls of the city and the temple, &amp;c.; and all this must be done before the Son of Man will make His\n  appearance. There will be wars and rumors of wars,<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> signs in the heavens<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115253\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115253)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115253)\">D&amp;C 102:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113062\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113062)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113062)\">D&amp;C 1:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113333\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113333)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113333)\">D&amp;C 20:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117113\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117113)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117113)\">JS&mdash;H 1:24-25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112858\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112858)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112858)\">Ether 3:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116260\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116260)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116260)\">D&amp;C 130:14-17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111710\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111710)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111710)\">Mosiah 26:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111805\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111805)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111805)\">Alma 5:49<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112532\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112532)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112532)\">3 Ne. 1:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114327\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114327)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114327)\">D&amp;C 69:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115901\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115901)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115901)\">D&amp;C 123:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108083\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108083)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108083)\">Matt. 16:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108345\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108345)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108345)\">Mark 9:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108489\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108489)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108489)\">Luke 9:27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108560\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108560)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108560)\">Luke 19:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116264\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116264)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116264)\">D&amp;C 130:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107336\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107336)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107336)\">Jer. 11:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116254\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116254)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116254)\">D&amp;C 130:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108222\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108222)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108222)\">Matt. 24:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116265\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116265)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116265)\">D&amp;C 130:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110811\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110811)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110811)\">Rev. 14:6-7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107595\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107595)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107595)\">Hosea 6:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108223\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108223)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108223)\">Matt. 24:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110814\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110814)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110814)\">Rev. 14:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109947\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109947)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109947)\">1 Thes. 5:4-5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108146\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108146)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108146)\">Matt. 21:44<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111253\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111253)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111253)\">2 Ne. 26:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107636\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107636)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107636)\">Amos 3:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107371\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107371)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107371)\">Jer. 30:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115595\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115595)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115595)\">D&amp;C 109:64<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114547\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114547)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114547)\">D&amp;C 77:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116466\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116466)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116466)\">D&amp;C 133:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107192\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107192)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107192)\">Isa. 44:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107489\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107489)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107489)\">Ezek. 37:21-28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107629\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107629)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107629)\">Joel 3:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107709\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107709)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107709)\">Zech. 13:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107711\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107711)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107711)\">Zech. 14:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106272\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106272)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106272)\">Deut. 3:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107503\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107503)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107503)\">Ezek. 47:8-9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107712\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107712)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107712)\">Zech. 14:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">24. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113841\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113841)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113841)\">D&amp;C 45:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}